Interface IRateQueryLookupPlugin<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface IRateQueryLookupPlugin<T>
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    A rate query lookup plugin provides the opportunity to implement custom failover logic in the even the primary lookup fails.
